rComments: Wilkie was the most brilliant and possibly the sanest professor in the dept in my time there.  He had the rare gift of combining modesty and charisma.  A mountain of knowledge and insight on romantic poetry.  Truly a nice man and a gifted teacher.  RIP Brian Wilkie.
